Maintainer: Yi Liu <yi.iu.biostat@gmail.com>
Description: The package implements the propensity score weighted estimators for several causal estimands from 
	     the classes of weighted ATE, weighted ATT and weighted ATC. We employ two ways for inference: 
	     (i) the more traditional estimate-then-plug-in for estimating propensity scores using the whole dataset 
	     and then plug-in the estimator formula to get the point estimates, and the variance is estimated by bootstrap;
	     and (ii) applying sample-splitting and cross-fitting and using the mean square of the estimated influence 
       	     functions of as the variance estimates. 
